  "text": "Nonetheless, with the continuous advancement in biomedical/life sciences, alternative molecular markers such as microRNAs (miRNAs) [CITATION_1] , microsatellite DNAs [CITATION_2] and improved DNA extraction methods may provide further opportunity for the development of more detection and diagnostic methods for epidemiological investigations.",
